ygData.subject: Re: Evil Characters
ygData.msgSnippet: Deeper in zone but beware since the patch they are a lot harder to kill because they upped the reists on the dwarven chicks. Naeeldar ... From: Fraal
ygData.messageBody:
Deeper in zone but beware since the patch they are a lot harder to kill because they upped the reists on the dwarven chicks.

Naeeldar

Subject: Re: [EQ_Necromancer] Evil Characters


in BB the dwarf chicks do you mean the ones by the docks? or are they deeper in the zone?

----- Original Message -----
From: Naeeldar
To: EQ_Necromancer@onelist.com
Sent: Monday, September 20, 1999 11:53 AM
Subject: Re: [EQ_Necromancer] Evil Characters


At level 34 you can go to East Karana and kill human guards or you can go to butcher and kill the dwarve chicks there. However you have to have jboots to do this.

Naeeldar
